channeldata.description: As of version 0.7.0, [reuse](https://pypi.org/project/reuse/) is used instead of fsfe-reuse.  If you still depend on fsfe-reuse, then you will automatically get the latest version of reuse. This dummy package depends on reuse.  If you depend on a specific older version of fsfe-reuse, then you will continue to get that version.
